5. When replacing widgets:
   - ALWAYS delete old widgets FIRST
   - Then create new widgets
   - Example: canvasAPI.deleteWidget('widget-1'); canvasAPI.addWidget(...);

6. Wrap ALL code in \`\`\`javascript blocks
    `;
  }

